PrecisAcceptance of the transfer from the Province of Ontario of the administration and control over a parcel of waterfront land situate in front of Bob's Island in the TOWN OF PARRY SOUND, which contains an area of some 5.022 hectares, which is to be used to accommodate a breakwater and to provide a basin for a small craft harbour and marina.
